					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="edit_view hidden">
				<h4 class="item_title">密码为6-20位，建议使用大小写字符、数字与特殊符号的组合</h4>
				<div class="edit_item">
					<form onsubmit="return false;" autocomplete="off">
						<div class="item_label">输入当前密码：</div>
						<div class="item_value">
							<input style="display: none;">
							<input type="password" name="old_password"><a class="forget_link" data-click="onClick" data-block="ACCOUNTINFO#SERCURITY" data-element="TOFOGETPWD" href="http://www.xuetangx.com/forget_password" target="_blank">忘记当前密码？</a>
						</div>
						<div class="item_label">输入新密码：</div>
						<div class="item_value">
							<input style="display: none;">
							<input type="password" name="new_password1">
						</div>
						<div class="item_label">再次输入新密码：</div>
						<div class="item_value">
							<input style="display: none;">
							<input type="password" name="new_password2">
						</div>
						<div class="item_hint">密码修改成功！</div>
						<div class="item_btns">
							<button class="confirm_btn save_password" data-click="onClick" data-block="ACCOUNTINFO#SERCURITY" data-element="TOSAVEPWD">确定修改</button>
